description:
200 PMP® Practice Questions in line with latest Guide to PMBoK® Fifth Edition with Detailed Explanations across the following Project Management Knowledge Areas:-

  • Project Management Framework
  • Project Integration Management
  • Project Scope Management
  • Project Time Management
  • Project Cost Management
  • Project Quality Management
  • Project Human Resource Management
  • Project Communication Management
  • Project Risk Management
  • Project Procurement Management
  • Project Stakeholder Management


Mock Questions are accompanied by a downloadable PMP® Exam Prep Assessment Sheet.

PMP® Aspirants should mark their scores on the Assessment Sheet for self-assessing PMP® Exam Preparedness.

They should be able to score at least 80% across all Knowledge Areas.

If an aspirant is scoring less than than 80%, he/she should refer the Guide to PMBoK® or any other good reference book for PMP® Exam Prep for that knowledge area.

In addition to PMP® Prep Mock Questions, participants will also get access to Downloadable ITTO Sheets(13 pages) & Project Management Process MindMaps (131 Pages) for quick revision before PMP® Exam.

Kindly Note - This course is not meant for participants who are already enrolled in KnowledgeWoods Pass PMP® - Project Management Professional Exam in 45 Days Course.
title: PMP® Exam Prep Practice Questions + ITTO Sheets & Mind Maps
